    <img src="baku eye.jpg" alt="Baku Eye" width="400" height="200">
</div>

<!-- Content Section 10: Surakhana Ship Museum -->
<div class="content-section">
    <div class="round-frame">
        <div>
            <h2>Surakhana Ship Museum</h2>
            <p>
                Surakhani Ship Museum (Suraxanı gəmi-muzeyi) is a museum in Baku reflecting the history of the development of shipping 
                and seafaring traditions in Azerbaijan.
            </p>
            <p>
                The museum, which is the first tanker museum in the world, provides information about the history of the Caspian Sea and Azerbaijan shipping, 
                as well as the activities of Azerbaijani sailors.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
